{
    "pages": [
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "Yet still you prefer the life of the dunya"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "when the akhira is better and longer lasting"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "This is certainly in the earlier texts"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "the texts of Ibrahim and Musa"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "Has news of the Overwhelmer reached you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "Some faces on that Day will be downcast"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "labouring, toiling endlessly"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "roasting in a red-hot Fire"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "drinking from a boiling spring"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "They have no food but a bitter thorny bush"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "which neither nourishes nor satisfies"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Some faces on that Day will be radiant"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "well-pleased with their efforts"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "in an elevated Garden"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "where no prattle is ever heard"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "In it is a gushing spring"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "and raised-up couches"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "and set-out goblets"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "and lined-up cushions"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "and spread-out rugs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Have they not looked at the camel — how it was created"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "and at the sky — how it was raised up"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "and at the mountains — how they were embedded"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "and at the earth — how it was smoothed out"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "So remind them! You are only a reminder"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "You are not in control of them"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "But as for anyone who turns away and is kafir"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "Allah will punish him with the Greatest Punishment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Certainly it is to Us they will return"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "Then their Reckoning is Our concern"
        }
    ]
}